title: Founder of promise-based viral social movement speaks Nov. 16 at MSU (Montana State University)
text: ( Source : Montana State University ) Alex Sheen, founder ofbecause I said I would,an international social movement and nonprofit dedicated to the betterment of humanity through promises made and kept, will speak at 7:30 p.m. Monday, Nov. 16,
